# Helm subchart tarballs are committed alongside Chart.lock so the
# ArgoCD repo-server does not have to reach every upstream Helm repo
# (bitnami, jetstack, victoriametrics, ...) on every reconcile — and
# so a single registry outage does not block a sync. Update procedure:
# `make chart-deps` then commit both Chart.lock and the new .tgz set.
